{"tid":2095093,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"各國現金紓困計劃","createTime":"2020-07-05T07:53:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T03:46:29.000Z","uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"702800c223af0f0aac14205bcfc4994acf126c30","tid":2095093,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T07:53:12.000Z","msg":"各國無差別現金紓困<br />\n<br />\n日本 每人10萬JPY (~7208HKD)  總計12.8兆JPY<br />\n香港 1萬HKD 總計710億HKD<br />\n韓國 中低收入戶(佔7成) 家庭計:1人40萬KRW 2人60萬KRW 3人80萬KRW 4人100萬KRW (1人~2585HKD)<br />\n澳門 1萬MOP (~9700HKD) 總計71億10萬MOP<br />\n新加坡 600新幣 (~3333HKD)<br />\n美國 年收入低於99000美元 (佔9成) 1200美元 (~9300HKD)<br />\n<br />\n好似好多人同時拎到兩個現金紓困<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/business-52450958\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-52450958&d=yjoviXv3QiMsqLwchXvj35uyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=a7a88b87\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-52450958&h=10ecba76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/news/business-52450958</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20200527000693-260109?chdtv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Fnewspapers%2F20200527000693-260109%3Fchdtv&d=yjoviXv3QiMsqLwchXvj35uyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=22e6e324\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20200527000693-260109?chdtv</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E5%90%84%E5%9C%8B%E7%B4%93%E5%9B%B0%E6%AF%94-%E6%AF%94-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%8B%82%E7%A0%B8gdp%E5%85%A9%E6%88%90-%E9%80%99%E5%85%AD%E5%80%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E6%89%8B%E7%AD%86-%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%E9%87%91-030408947.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.stock.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E5%2590%2584%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25B4%2593%25E5%259B%25B0%25E6%2